text: Estanislao Artal (5 September 1912 - September 1967) was a Spanish swimmer. He competed in the men's 4 × 200 metre freestyle relay event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1912 births Category:1967 deaths Category:Spanish male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Spain Category:Swimmers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Swimmers from Barcelona
